@startuml 图4-1 登录认证时序图
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontColor #000000
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "用户" as User
participant "Vue前端" as Vue
participant "Gateway\nAuthFilter" as GW
participant "edu-auth\nTokenController" as Auth
participant "SysLoginService" as SLS
participant "sys_user\n(MySQL)" as DB
participant "Redis\nlogin_tokens" as Redis

User -> Vue : 输入用户名密码\n点击登录
Vue -> GW : POST /auth/login\n{username, password}
GW -> GW : 检查白名单\n/auth/login放行
GW -> Auth : 转发请求
Auth -> SLS : login(username, password)
SLS -> DB : SELECT * FROM sys_user\nWHERE user_name=?
DB --> SLS : 返回用户记录

alt 用户不存在或密码错误
  SLS --> Auth : 返回错误
  Auth --> Vue : 401 登录失败
else 验证通过
  SLS -> Redis : 加载用户角色和权限
  Redis --> SLS : 权限集合
  SLS --> Auth : LoginUser对象
  Auth -> Auth : 生成UUID作为user_key
  Auth -> Auth : JwtUtils.createToken(\nuser_key, userId, username)
  Auth -> Redis : SET login_tokens:{user_key}\n= LoginUser, TTL=720min
  Auth --> Vue : 200 OK {token: jwt_string}
  Vue -> Vue : 存储token到localStorage
  Vue --> User : 跳转首页
end

note over GW, Redis
  后续请求:
  Vue 自动携带 Authorization: Bearer {jwt}
  AuthFilter 解析JWT → 查Redis → 放行
end note

@enduml
